With profound sadness, we reflect on the sorrow that weighs on our hearts today. When our father, Dr. Prathap C. Reddy, entrusted Apollo Hospitals to us, it was with a deep belief in respect, compassion, and the sacred duty of healing. The recent attacks on our fellow caregivers, particularly women doctors, have shattered us. In a country where doctors have always been revered, this erosion of trust is heartbreaking. As a nation, we must confront this painful reality together. At Apollo, we remain steadfast in our commitment to protect, heal, and uphold the dignity and safety of all who serve and seek care within our walls. 

#Apollohospitals #ApolloPharmacy
